strings.Value: "I'm glad I wasn't wrong about you. Onward! To victory!"
"Smother me with kisses? I might just hold you to that!"
"I like your enthusiasm, but let's cut out the inappropriate advances."
"Say that one more time and you'll get a punch in the face."

{n}Regongar sizes up the Stag Lord's fort from afar, then looks at you and shakes his head with a smirk.{/n} "Well... We're here. A handful of lunatics are about to assault a whole fortress stuffed with bandits armed to the teeth, who have been keeping the entire region under their boot."

"Truth be told, I wouldn't bet a copper bit on us right now. You'd have to be a complete psycho to do this. So... Damn right I'm with you, ha ha ha hmm! If we somehow make it out of this alive, I'll smother you with kisses!"
"Ha ha hmm... Now I definitely have enough reasons to make it through alive. All right — let's get to it!"
"I'm joking, I'm joking! So, you ready to get to it? Let's show those scoundrels who owns that fortress!"
"Hey, hey, easy! I was only joking, ha ha! You want to punch someone — punch the Stag Lord's bandits!"
